title: Episode 181: Aliens with dickginas (Feat. Shauna Brooks & Chanel Ayana)
itunes:title: Episode 181: Aliens with dickginas (Feat. Shauna Brooks & Chanel Ayana)
description:
Shauna Brooks and Chanel Ayana join the ladies of Lip Service and open up about hardships from their life. Shauna expresses her thankfulness to her fans for helping her most while she was homeless. Chanel details the mental abuse she would face from her previous man. Shauna addresses the rumors surrounding Stevie J, and much more. Enjoy! ***LIVE SHOW ALERT*** When: Thursday, March 28, 2019 at 7:30pm Where: Carolines on Broadway - NYC Link: https://www.ticketweb.com/event/lip-service-live-carolines-on-broad
